settings.description: Mario Falls down after taking on the airship he was on, he finds himself in this area, he will need to be careful and not die! Cloud Tower is next.
The 'Ultimate" airship is hare! You must board it and get through it, then fight Boom Boom, the airship creator! Don't die or you will be forced to restart, he is a lot harder this time!
Mario finds himself in the Underground Bunker after taking on the air fleet, he must get through it without any mistakes. Or else...
You and your crew are on vacation when a anomaly strikes your ship and you and your crew evacuates! You find your ship safe but 4 of your crewmates are missing! Find them! Based off: VVVVVV
Mario finds himself in a World with water, can he escape to cloud land? Base of operations of M and L are ahead, so be quick!
Mario Adventures Through the clouds to get to Bowsers Castle, nowhere near yet...
Roto-discs are like Fire Bars, but with much more room to dodge! Just make sure to keep your wits about you; they're a lot faster, too!
